title: Favorite Disney Memories | World Princess Week

author: Disney
description:
Celebrate Disney Princesses with a one-of-a-kind concert filmed in front of a live audience at Disneyland Park. Beloved Princess voice talent including Jodi Benson (voice of Ariel, "The Little Mermaid"), Auli‘i Cravalho (voice of Moana, "Moana 2"), Paige O’Hara (voice of Belle, "Beauty and the Beast"), and Anika Noni Rose (voice of Tiana, "The Princess and the Frog"), perform timeless songs, joined by hosts Ginnifer Goodwin and Susan Egan in front of the iconic Sleeping Beauty Castle.
